properties.description: Prahran Square is a 10,000 square metre urban parkland and is the City of Stonnington's transformation of the old Cato Street car park into a dynamic and inviting public space. Prahran Square celebrates community, arts and culture, playing host to an array of events, live performances and showcasing works by local artists.
